  <info>
    <title></title>
    <meta name="maintainer" content="tbazant@suse.com" its:translate="no"/>
    <abstract>
      <para>
        The following chart illustrates the installation process of
        &productname;. It outlines the following possible scenarios:
      </para>
      <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            You have clean cluster nodes prepared without a supported Linux
            operating system installed.
          </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            You have a supported Linux operating system and &kube; distribution
            installed on cluster nodes.
          </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            You have &rancherprime; and all supportive components installed on
            the &kube; cluster and are prepared to install the required
            applications from the &ailibrary;.
          </para>
        </listitem>
      </itemizedlist>
    </abstract>
  </info>
  <figure xml:id="fg-ai-installation-flowchart" condition="deployment_standard">
    <title>&productname; installation process</title>
    <mediaobject>
      <imageobject role="fo">
